Interface Capability

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Adaptable, EObject, Marked, ModelElement, NamedElement, Notifier, Period
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    Decision, EngineeredCapability, Feature, Issue, Release
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    CapabilityImpl, DecisionImpl, EngineeredCapabilityImpl, FeatureImpl, IssueImpl, ReleaseImpl

    public interface Capability
extends NamedElement, Period
    A representation of the model object 'Capability'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Required By
    • Available

        EList<Issue> getRequiredBy()
        Returns the value of the 'Required By' reference list. The list contents are of type Issue. Issues requiring this capability.

      • isAvailable

        boolean isAvailable()
        Returns the value of the 'Available' attribute. Indicates that this capability is available and [issues](Issue.html) which require it are workable, unless they have other unavailable requirements.
        Returns:
        the value of the 'Available' attribute.
        See Also:
        setAvailable(boolean), EngineeringPackage.getCapability_Available()
